CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: TuanChe Ltd is an omnichannel automotive marketplace in China. The company operates in one operating segment of providing auto shows, special promotion events services, and virtual dealership, online marketing services and others. It organizes auto shows, which aim at facilitating transactions between consumers and auto dealers that includes auto dealers, automakers, and automotive service providers. It provides services through its online platform and offline events. Geographically the company generates revenue from the China market.
